Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:09.16,Episode Title,Sign 0203,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(1402.5,230.5)}Món Don \NYên Lặng, \N Món Don \NHùng Biện
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:06.14,Main Dialogue,Guys,0,0,0,,À, Nikumi đấu với Don ken ấy hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:11.19,Main Dialogue,Guys,0,0,0,,Tội nghiệp bọn Don ken, xui sao mà \Nlại rớt vào tầm ngắm của Nakiri Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.69,Main Dialogue,Guys,0,0,0,,Này, cậu đọc bản tin Tootsuki chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.03,Main Dialogue,Guys,0,0,0,,Đối thủ đã thay đổi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:18.15,Main Dialogue,Guys,0,0,0,,Coi nè, là tên lính mới đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.73,Main Dialogue,Guys,0,0,0,,Yukihira Souma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:23.70,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0,0,0,,Đây là nguyên liệu và dụng cụ cần trong trận đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.22,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0,0,0,,Anh đã mang đủ những thứ cậu yêu cầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:28.79,Main Dialogue,S,0,0,0,,Ừ. Cám ơn anh, Konishi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.78,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0,0,0,,Cậu không chợp mắt tí nào sao, Yukihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:36.96,Main Dialogue,S,0,0,0,,Em còn phải làm thêm chút nước sốt nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.68,Main Dialogue,S,0,0,0,,Mà em cũng ngủ được cỡ hai tiếng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.79,Italics Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Nhiều người quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.92,Main Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,S-Souma-kun, c-cậu không được cuống...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.78,Main Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,K-K-không được cuống nha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.65,Main Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,N-Những lúc thế này,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.27,Main Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,cậu nên viết chữ “nhân” lên lòng bàn tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.20,Main Dialogue,S,0,0,0,,{\an8}Được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:01.91,Main Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Viết lên đó nhá.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.91,Main Dialogue,S,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tadokoro nên nuốt nó mau đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:02.49,Main Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Hả?
