Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.92,Main Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Cậu phải nấu ăn trước mặt nhiều người như vậy mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:08.87,Main Dialogue,S,0,0,0,,Không hề.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.08,Main Dialogue,S,0,0,0,,Những chuyện thế này
